>> title: BBQ Lentil Bowl
>> cuisine: American
>> tags: bowl, quick-assembly, vegan, gluten-free, soy-free
>> servings: 1

-- This is an assembly recipe - all components should be prepped ahead.
-- Assembly time: 5 minutes

Scoop @../components/grains/creamy-mashed-potatoes{1%cup}(warmed) into #bowl{} (or use rice).

Top with @../components/proteins/bbq-lentils{3/4%cup}(heated).

Add @coleslaw mix{1/2%cup} on the side.

Drizzle with extra @BBQ sauce{1%tbsp}.

Add @pickles{2%tbsp}(optional) on the side.

-- Hearty American comfort food with a plant-based twist
